    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115800/extras/3c65d76e50a3eadbc5f99843fae5f4e9.poster.avif?t=1724342322\" width=720 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115800/extras/3c65d76e50a3eadbc5f99843fae5f4e9.webm?t=1724342322\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115800/extras/3c65d76e50a3eadbc5f99843fae5f4e9.mp4?t=1724342322\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>《<strong>寻找莫西</strong>》是一款开放世界的单人第三人称角色扮演游戏，关于寻找你的猫。<br><br><strong>成功在Kickstarter上筹资！</strong><br><br>在与你的猫一起度过宁静的露营之旅时，有一天你醒来发现他不见了。这次寻找引导你深入了解你的环境以及它与猫的关系的深奥之处。当你探索景观和城市时，你决定成为什么样的角色将决定你的寻找是如何毁灭或和平的。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115800/extras/d6a4b2f640e8435f90f6220e4ac5ea0f.poster.avif?t=1724342322\" width=720 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115800/extras/d6a4b2f640e8435f90f6220e4ac5ea0f.webm?t=1724342322\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115800/extras/d6a4b2f640e8435f90f6220e4ac5ea0f.mp4?t=1724342322\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特点</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">[]适用于<i>荒野之息</i>、<i>羊角模拟器</i>和<i>外星荒野</i>的粉丝。</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">[]招募猫来对抗生物和压迫者。</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">[]随时随地前往任何地方，但寻找/解锁物品将使探索变得更容易。</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">[]各种互动战利品可供不同的游戏方式使用。</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">[]在探索充满独特角色的沉浸式环境中寻找你的猫，这些角色可能会提供信息来帮助你。</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">[]不包含血腥元素的选项。</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>你可以抚摸任何一只猫。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115800/extras/53c3bf596c6f6aed2caf8622b916735d.poster.avif?t=1724342322\" width=720 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115800/extras/53c3bf596c6f6aed2caf8622b916735d.webm?t=1724342322\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115800/extras/53c3bf596c6f6aed2caf8622b916735d.mp4?t=1724342322\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
